						<summary>

						<p>On the east wall of the Bhairava shrine in the Vālīśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Rājarāja III. Year 27: 1242-43 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This inscription records the gift of 11 <hi rend="italic">māḍai</hi> by Koṭṭū[r] Vaḍukaṉ for burning a twilight lamp to the deity Tirukkārikarai-piḷḷaiyār of Niṉṟaiyūr-nāḍu, a district of Kuṉṟavattana-kkōṭṭam, a sub-division of Jayaṅgoṇḍaśōḻa-maṇḍalam.</p>						

						</summary>
